#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"Nature21 is a smooth and refreshing WordPress theme. It is built for anyone "
"who wants to share stories about the environment and the outdoors. It "
"highlights the wilderness and landscape around us while giving your site "
"clean sections to showcase scenery, habitat details, and ecosystem "
"conservation projects. The theme suits countryside tours, flora and fauna "
"blogs, greenery drives, and content that celebrates mother earth. You can "
"present terrain shots, biosphere studies, and natural world updates with "
"ease. Nature21 also supports galleries for wilds, open air adventures, "
"woodlands, meadows, and fields. With simple setup, fast loading, and mobile-"
"ready pages, Nature21 helps you build a clear and engaging eco-friendly "
"website. Documentation : xxx-xxx-xxx"
msgstr ""

